    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110710/extras/fa49a7e18daff57a11004f91c606900a.avif?t=1689121035\" width=616 height=116 /></span><br><br>Prepare to immerse yourself in the thrill of VoxSys, the cutting-edge arena shooter that seamlessly blends cooperative PvP combat with dynamic building mechanics. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110710/extras/deb014b30dab209e3f795d520b8b8f61.poster.avif?t=1689121035\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110710/extras/deb014b30dab209e3f795d520b8b8f61.webm?t=1689121035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110710/extras/deb014b30dab209e3f795d520b8b8f61.mp4?t=1689121035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Your cover is not only your protection but also your weapon - master it to outsmart your opponents and emerge victorious. Engage in heart-pounding battles alongside your team, utilizing a vast array of futuristic weapons and power-ups to annihilate your opponents and earn the coveted title of Intergalactic Champion. But be warned, the fully destructible sci-fi setting demands strategic thinking and expert timing.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110710/extras/dfc1b7f1bff8c300e3de815f7dfbd243.poster.avif?t=1689121035\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110710/extras/dfc1b7f1bff8c300e3de815f7dfbd243.webm?t=1689121035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110710/extras/dfc1b7f1bff8c300e3de815f7dfbd243.mp4?t=1689121035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can destroy or build any part of the maps and place special blocks for further interactions which makes the game more dynamic.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110710/extras/ec880f641c51a7c211fcbc239b693aa1.poster.avif?t=1689121035\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110710/extras/ec880f641c51a7c211fcbc239b693aa1.webm?t=1689121035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110710/extras/ec880f641c51a7c211fcbc239b693aa1.mp4?t=1689121035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Become the star of the show as the audience and commentators follow your every move and call out your impressive shots and strategies. VoxSys is more than just a game - it's an intense and immersive event that will keep you on the edge of your seat. So what are you waiting for? It's time to build, fight, and dominate in VoxSys!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110710/extras/35f5faeb23d08836d3d86837b92d71b9.poster.avif?t=1689121035\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110710/extras/35f5faeb23d08836d3d86837b92d71b9.webm?t=1689121035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110710/extras/35f5faeb23d08836d3d86837b92d71b9.mp4?t=1689121035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With our map editor, you can easily create your own custom maps and submit them to be added to the official map pool. Imagine seeing your very own creation being played by gamers all around the world!",
